rComments: One of the BEST profs I've had at UofT. Passionate, engaging and caring, Prof Cameron clearly cares a great deal about her profession, as well as her students. There is a lot of material to learn in lectures/recordings, but she explains everything with excellent clarity. She is also very accessible/helpful outside of class. A model for all profs.
The course I took with Hilary was super hard and it was definitely reflected in her grading as well. Despite the difficulty, the class was still enjoyable because Hilary was fantastic!

rComments: Hilary is by far the best professor I've had in my time at UofT.
